Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take the good things and the bad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.35,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nee ii koto mo warui koto mo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Add them all together
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.29,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subete tashite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.83,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divide it by two and live well
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.83,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ni de watte umaku ikite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:21.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to transcend time
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:21.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Toki o koetai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naše interview je pomaly u konca.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.30,0:01:53.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale mám na členov\NASKu ešte jednu otázku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si myslíte o vašom prvom albume?\NSte s ním spokojní?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Len sme začali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sme nenásytní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdy nebudeme spokojní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sme spokojní, znamená to,\Nže je koniec.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Váš producent je Touma Seguchi,\Npredali ste toľko albumov,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.69,0:02:21.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a stále nie ste spokojní?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočne ste nenásytná skupina.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.66,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Páčia sa mi. Sú dobrí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.83,0:02:32.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že to\Npočujem od vás, Kaoruko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ste príliš skromný,\Nna tak charizmatického producenta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teším sa na váš koncert.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.98,0:02:40.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vaše prvé vystúpenie, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bude to úžasné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A otvorenie koncertu\Nzaháji skupina...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.16,0:02:51.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Luck?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.36,0:02:57.19,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, má ich na starosti\NSakano z našej spoločnosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.50,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A akí sú?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ktovie? Uvidíme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi, meškáš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.58,0:03:19.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah tak, preto ste ich vybrali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal som sa stretnúť\Ns prezidentom spoločnosti,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ukázať mu jednu, dve pesničky,\Nktoré ste napísali.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.49,0:03:27.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne ste dostali príležitosť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}"Kúpanie vo fontáne zakázané.\NPark Shinjuku."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne ste dostali príležitosť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}"Kúpanie vo fontáne zakázané.\NPark Shinjuku."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mohol to byť váš veľký úspech!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mohol to byť váš veľký úspech!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tento náš plán...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo úplne zničil...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakano, to len fantazíruješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A čo keď fantazírujem?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíme sa vnucovať\Na žiadať o pomoc...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.38,0:03:51.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme inú možnosť,\Nako sa vnucovať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.58,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vašu pesničku ste vôbec nedokončili!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.19,0:04:00.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shindo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, o chvíľu máme koncert.\NVidieť, že si pod tlakom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pekne si to unáhlil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je? Nepáči sa ti?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.21,0:04:19.51,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, zatiaľ nebudem komentovať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokým neuvidím celý text.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichi, úmyselne si\Nprišiel neskoro, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Po pravde,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.09,0:04:37.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stretol som po ceste korytnačku,\Nktorú týrali deti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak som jej pomohol...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.76,0:04:42.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A potom ťa zobrala\Ndo podmorského paláca?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Presne!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri, poklad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.94,0:04:52.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cením si, čo pre nás Sakano robí...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.71,0:04:55.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a Seguchi je úžasný producent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.68,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokonca hral kedysi v Nittle Grasper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.88,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal by si si nájsť spoločnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dievča.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to s tým má spoločné?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.13,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poznáš nejaké?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...to je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nejde o to!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.43,0:05:14.76,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pre tvoje dobro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dôverujem ti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.20,0:05:22.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že máš talent\Na snažíš sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.91,0:05:26.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale každý sa raz unaví.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Porozmýšľaj nad tým.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zoznámim ťa s niekym.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám ho však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.26,0:05:41.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím talent.\NMám na to talent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, uvidíme sa zajtra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.94,0:05:51.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Príď na čas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.08,0:06:04.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rodený talent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snažiť sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale na úspech to nestačí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dievča.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Možno má pravdu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.01,0:06:29.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To si napísal ty?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.74,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako z materskej škôlky.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To má byť milostná pieseň?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Máš nulový talent.\NVzdaj to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusel si to tak povedať?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.68,0:07:43.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.12,0:07:44.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si ju nedokončil?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nechcem ti nadávať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ak si nešvihneme...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tak sme skončili!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zlyhal som ako manažér!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám inú možnosť...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.33,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte, že som vás sklamal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.47,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj! Stoj!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.47,0:08:03.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Včera sa niečo prihodilo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Včera? Po tom, čo som odišiel?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:11.84,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.64,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeden strašidelný chlápik to videl.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo videl? Že močíš v kríkoch?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Ten text!\NText našej pesničky!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.45,0:08:26.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bol to strašný hlupák.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rovno do očí mi povedal,\Nže mám nulový talent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.09,0:08:32.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Že by som mal skončiť.\N"Ako z materskej škôlky"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš, že to bolo kruté?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je všetko?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš všetko?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.01,0:08:45.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, aj Sakuma Ryuichi raz povedal:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Čo je talent? Niečo na jedenie?"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.31,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On je výnimočný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.88,0:08:54.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Taký talentovaný... Akoby žil v inom svete.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako Boh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.22,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak to už chodí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.22,0:09:04.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš byť naštvaný\Nkvôli nejakému hlupákovi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nejde o to!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mal som pocit,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,že ma nenávidí,\Npritom sme sa videli prvýkrát.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netráp sa tým.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netrápim!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.77,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem len, aby sa mi ospravedlnil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trápi ťa to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trápi ho to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudni na to.\NNemáme na tieto hlúposti čas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem na to zabudnúť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.86,0:09:41.09,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože bol... tak úžasný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri na to super auto!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zahraničné?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.32,0:10:10.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stoj!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak chceš spáchať samovraždu,\Nnájdi si iné auto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sopliak jeden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.30,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tu máš, uterák.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.03,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Máš proti mne niečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To teda mám!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skoro som kvôli\Ntebe zničil auto!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.92,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevravím o tom!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vtedy, keď sme sa stretli v parku...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínam si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.45,0:11:38.12,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínaš si?!\NPo tom všetko, čo si mi povedal?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.12,0:11:41.35,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš sa zabiť?\NAlebo odo mňa niečo chceš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vyber si, ty sopliak.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.56,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moje meno je Shindo Shuichi!\NNie sopliak...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:47.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je mi jedno,\Nvieš o kom je reč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.89,0:11:55.16,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, nevyzeráš ako niekto,\Nkto by chcel spáchať samovraždu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.20,0:11:56.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:12:01.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som ťa len znovu vidieť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.94,0:12:05.93,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak je to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.80,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naštvala ťa moja kritika?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.25,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na tú pesničku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.25,0:12:10.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vravel si, že si nespomínaš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Klamal som, hlupáčik.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ako by som mohol\Nzabudnúť na tak úbohý text?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Úbohý, úbohý", to je všetko, čo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spamätaj sa! Keď poviem\Nnulový talent, myslím tým nulový.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.20,0:12:31.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, v poriadku. Žiaden problém.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:34.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale prosím ťa,\Nna tieto veci už nemyslím.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.57,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grasper je minulosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.57,0:12:40.10,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bez Ryuichiho nemôže\Nbyť Nittle Grasper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.65,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre. Všetko budete mať pripravené.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pán prezident...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.19,0:12:51.98,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uprednostním ASK.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To je najefektívnejšia stratégia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomu rozumiem, ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.06,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakano.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi to ľúto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokončil som ju!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.38,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shindo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo tesné, Sakano.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pán prezident...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.83,0:13:29.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tie rozbité dvere opravíte.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, neviem čo ťa k tomu prinútilo,\Nale potešil si nás!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gratulujem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, čo je s tebou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neveríš si?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.04,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Verím! Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.08,0:13:49.24,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pohádal som sa s tým\Narogantným chlapíkom,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tak ma naštval, že som sa\Nrozhodol tú pesničku dokončiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pripadám si úboho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.32,0:13:57.05,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už zase ten chlapík...\NKto to je?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.11,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten chlap.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.43,0:14:02.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nespýtal som sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.63,0:14:08.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som sa spýtať,\Nale myslím, že by mi to nepovedal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.10,0:14:12.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priťahuje ťa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.44,0:14:17.27,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celý čas o ňom rozprávaš.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým chceš povedať?! Je to muž!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.61,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevyberieš si, do koho sa zamiluješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.85,0:14:27.75,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale... Vždy som ťa mal len pre seba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.35,0:14:35.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A teraz si si našiel iného chlapa.\NBude mi smutno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.99,0:14:39.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hiro, ty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, nikdy som si to nevšimol.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem len, aby si bol šťastný.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choď sa mu zdôveriť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.48,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš kde býva, nie?\NNemusíš vedieť, ako sa volá.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.36,0:15:10.99,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Som taký hlupák. Strašný hlupák.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.42,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, myslím, že každý čitateľ\Nbude mať odlišný názor,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.67,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nemôžem to objektívne posúdiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.40,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten chlap...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.54,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem. Ale pán Yuki,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.54,0:15:29.45,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,vaše romány sú v podstate\Nvždy milostné príbehy,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.97,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aj keď sú plné krvi a násilia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.32,0:15:37.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asi máte pravdu.\NLáska predsa nie je všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.46,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V podstate píšem knihy, lebo...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.39,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Eiri.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.23,0:15:49.43,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Populárny autor milostných\Npribehov, hlavne u žien.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.94,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Spisovateľ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Už rozumiem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.04,0:15:58.07,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto bol k tvojím textom tak kritický.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.17,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.89,gravi_opening,,0000,0000,0000,,With a frightened look in my eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.89,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte mi to zdržanie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.22,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With a frightened look in my eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.69,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I take my impatience
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.28,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I take my impatience
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Kam šiel Shindo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.63,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I toss it to the capricious winds
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.85,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I toss it to the capricious winds
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.85,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zdôveriť sa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.03,0:16:17.33,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the cracked pavement
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.06,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the cracked pavement
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.79,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the cracked pavement
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.93,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The signal that melted away
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.49,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only leaves a scar behind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before the sleepy noise erases tomorrow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.84,0:16:40.22,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I chase the footsteps, echoing with ambition
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.22,0:16:45.76,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't stop anywhere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.76,0:16:51.66,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore the unfulfilled\Nemotions and get over them
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.66,0:16:57.37,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the trembling world of shyness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.17,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for the escape route
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.14,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towards the place I'll arrive at
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.44,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towards the place I'll arrive at
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.44,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tu robíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.44,0:17:02.84,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towards the place I'll arrive at
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.02,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak veľmi si ma chcel vidieť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To určite?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.55,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prišiel som ťa vyzvať!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.26,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi jedno, či si spisovateľ.\NPríď na môj koncert a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri, počkaj!\NJe mi jedno, či si spisovateľ.\NPríď na môj koncert a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.23,0:17:25.96,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eiri!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.37,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je to dieťa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.37,0:17:35.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, poďme, Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes máme rande.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.78,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je taký zlatučký.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.15,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kto ti je tu z...?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.15,0:17:50.14,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem si pomôcť,\Nsi tak tvrdohlavý, Shuichi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.95,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preto si taký zlatý, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte slovo a si mŕtvy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.33,0:18:01.53,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem. Takže je pre teba\Ndôležitejší ako ja.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.11,0:18:08.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hlupák.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.81,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Určite je to v poriadku?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.18,0:18:18.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.49,0:18:25.32,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je! Ranil si ju!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.52,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asi hej. Je naštvaná.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.69,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ale tým lepšie pre teba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si šťastný, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým chceš povedať?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.90,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Priťahujem ťa, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.91,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak? Kedy máš ten koncert?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.01,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sedemnásteho. Zepp Tokyo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mám si ju vypočuť?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.41,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tú mizernú pesničku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.28,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je? Nepoprieš to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.29,0:19:03.23,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovor mi,\Nže ma skutočne miluješ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.89,0:19:04.70,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To nie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.60,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, nájdi si niekoho iného.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.36,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám chuť sa ťahať s inými mužmi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.94,0:19:12.63,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stoj!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.20,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, počkaj chvíľu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.21,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To určite! Kto po tebe chcel,\Naby si prišiel na koncert!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.08,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netvár sa tak namyslene!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.72,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stále len kritizuješ moju pesničku,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.71,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ale pochopil si vôbec jej text?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.49,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si myslíš, že je nanič,\Nprečo ju neignoruješ?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.62,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A vyrývaš!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.73,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musíš stále ponižovať?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.86,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo neustále provokuješ?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.83,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sklapni.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.87,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Si otravný,\N"Prečo? Prečo?"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.68,0:19:57.34,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiež sa ma to stále pýta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.18,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tak sa spýtam ja teba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo za mnou stále chodíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.35,0:20:06.29,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa na mňa tak pozeraš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.00,titulky,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.02,0:20:46.36,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amidst a noisy crowd of people
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.02,0:20:46.36,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nigiyaka na hitogomi ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:51.10,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The murmured words melt away
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:51.10,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokeru tsubuyaki ga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.47,0:20:55.60,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scattered at my feet
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.47,0:20:55.60,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ashimoto ni chirabatta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.67,0:21:00.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are memories that become blurred by it
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.67,0:21:00.23,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Omoide nijimaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.68,0:21:06.22,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wander aimlessly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.68,0:21:06.22,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi aruku
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.22,0:21:09.81,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the brilliant lights of the town
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.22,0:21:09.81,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machi no kagayaki wa
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.45,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glaring one way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.39,0:21:19.02,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Illuminate me, on the verge of freezing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.39,0:21:19.02,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoesou na boku o terasu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:26.00,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cold time brings dreams from the skies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:26.00,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumetai toki ga yume o furaseru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.00,0:21:30.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they slip through my fingers
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.00,0:21:30.67,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kono te no naka o surinukete
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.67,0:21:35.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Counting my wishes, when I wake up
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.67,0:21:35.48,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Negai kazoe mezameta toki ni
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.48,0:21:43.52,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are there in the wavering vision
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.48,0:21:43.52,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yureru maboroshi ni kimi ga utsuru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.52,0:21:49.12,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A faint silhouette that guides me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.52,0:21:49.12,gravi_opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boku o michibiku kasuka na shiruetto
